Actor Francis Duru is celebrating his 19th wedding anniversary with wife, Adokiye. The actor described her as an amazing woman, elegant stallion and great midwife. He blessed the day he set eyes on her as he appreciated her for being selfless and vowed his undying love for her. Duru also expressed gratitude to God while he coveted prayers for all and sundry as he celebrates almost 2 decades of marital bless with his wife. Sharing a photo with his wife, the thespian wrote: “Stuck 4 Eva……HIs Design..Blessed with 3 most wonderful kids….HIS FAVOUR..sustained ….BY HIS GRACE…   Nollywood mourns Osmond Gbadebo     Why I can’t be angry with my husband for long-Khafi     Actress Stephanie Linus welcomes second child   “HELD BY THE NAIL…for 19years to an amazing woman…my elegant stallion…I bless the day I found you.. “You fill the essence fueled from on high..my great midwife..tnx for being you and being there for us…thanks Dox..no one but you…my undying love I vow 4 Eva… “We bless God good people ..it’s our wedding anniversary ..your prayers will be cherished most…may the good Lord bless you all abundantly.” Duru and Adokiye attended the University of Port Harcourt. They got married in 2003 and are blessed with three children.